'''Ishimwe Herniette''' Umukinnyi w’ikipe y’[[Rwanda Nziza|igihugu y’u Rwanda]] mu bagore mu mukino wa Cricket, ujya i Dubai muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Abarabu (UAE) aho yitabira irushanwa mpuzamahanga  “Fairbreak Global Invitational” ryitabiriwe n’amakipe menshi agizwe n’abakinnyi b’ibihangange ku [[Isi|Isi.]]

== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
 
'''Ishimwe Herniette''' (wavutse 1 Mutarama 2003) usanzwe ari Visi Kapiteni w’ikipe y’igihugu ya Cricket ari mu ikipe yitwa "The Barmy Army Team",<ref>https://imvahonshya.co.rw/?p=9661</ref> aho aba ari kumwe n’abandi bakinnyi  bakomeye ku  Isi  bari mu ikipe nkuko bikorwa mu mukino wa Cricket.<ref>http://www.rebero.co.rw/2022/04/30/henriette-ishimwe-agiye-gukinira-ikipe-yitwa-the-barmy-army-team/</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/116765/cricket-umunyarwandakazi-ishimwe-herniette-agiye-gukinana-nibihangange-ku-isi-muiri-uyu-mu-116765.html</ref>
