=== AMARUSHANWA YITABIRIYE ===
'''Ishimwe Herniette''' yitabirye amarushwanwa atadukanye ku [[isi]] muri 26 kamena 2019 ryabereye muri [[Nijeriya|nigeria]] i [[Abuja|Abija]] muri National Stadium, umukino ubanza bahuye nikipe y'igihugu ya [[Nijeriya|Nigeria]]. Nanone bongeye kwitabira irushanwa i [[harare]], muri [[Zimbabwe]] muri Gicurasi 2019,ku mucyino 2 batsinze [[Mozambike]] 48 kuri 40, aha yabaye umukinnyi w'umukino. bakomeza batsinda undi mukino wabahuje na [[Tanzaniya|Tanzanie]].<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henriette_Ishimwe</ref><ref>https://www.espncricinfo.com/player/henriette-ishimwe-1172634</ref>
 

